ose absolute values within 1° (or 1.5° if Luminary). This equatorial tension is often more lasting and intimate than a longitudinal opposition.'\n                  : 'Deux planètes d\\'hémisphères opposés (N/S) avec des valeurs absolues proches à moins de 1° (ou 1.5° si Luminaire). Cette tension équatoriale est souvent plus durable et plus intime qu\\'une opposition en longitude.'}\n            </p>`;\n            html += `<table>\n                <tr><th>${isEN ? 'Planet 1' : 'Planète 1'}</th><th style=\"text-align:center\">${isEN ? 'Decl. 1' : 'Décl. 1'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Planet 2' : 'Planète 2'}</th><th style=\"text-align:center\">${isEN ? 'Decl. 2' : 'Décl. 2'}</th><th style=\"text-align:center\">${isEN ? 'Orb' : 'Orbe'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Note' : 'Note'}</th></tr>`;\n            contreParalleles.forEach(p => {\n                const lumRow = p.hasLuminaire ? ' style=\"background:#e8f0fe;\"' : '';\n                const lumNote = p.hasLuminaire\n                    ? `<span class=\"tag tag-contrepara\" style=\"font-size:0.85em;\">★ ${isEN ? 'Luminary (extended orb 1.5°)' : 'Luminaire (orbe étendu 1.5°)'}</span>`\n                    : `<span style=\"color:#64748b;font-size:0.85em;\">Standard</span>`;\n                html += `<tr${lumRow}>\n                    <td><strong>${p.p1}</strong></td>\n                    <td style=\"text-align:center;font-weight:bold;color:#1F3864\">${(p.decl1 ?? 0) >= 0 ? \"+\" : \"\"}${(p.decl1 ?? 0).toFixed(4)}°</td>\n                    <td><strong>${p.p2}</strong></td>\n                    <td style=\"text-align:center;font-weight:bold;color:#1F3864\">${(p.decl2 ?? 0) >= 0 ? \"+\" : \"\"}${(p.decl2 ?? 0).toFixed(4)}°</td>\n                    <td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>${p.orb}°</strong></td>\n                    <td>${lumNote}</td>\n                </tr>`;\n            });\n            html += `</table>`;\n        }\n\n        if (paralleles.length === 0 && contreParalleles.length === 0) {\n            html += `<p class=\"empty-msg\">${isEN ? `No parallel or contra-parallel detected within defined orb limits (${1.0}° standard / ${1.5}° Luminaries).` : `Aucun parallèle ni contre-parallèle détecté dans les limites d'orbe définies (${1.0}° standard / ${1.5}° Luminaires).`}</p>`;\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n// ── Étoiles Fixes — Influences stellaires ──\nif (etoileMatches.length > 0 || etoileCuspMatches.length > 0) {\n    html += `<h2 class=\"section-title page-break\">${isEN ? 'Fixed Stars — Stellar Influences' : 'Étoiles Fixes — Influences Stellaires'}</h2>`;\n    html += `<p style=\"color:#5d4037;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 15px;padding:12px 16px;background:#fff8e1;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #ffb300;font-size:0.95em;\">\n        ${isEN\n          ? 'Orbs applied: <strong>±2°</strong> for Aldebaran, Sirius, Regulus, Spica, Antares (royal/major stars) — <strong>±1°</strong> for Algol, Pleiades, Vega, Fomalhaut. Precision: <strong style=\"color:#5d4037\">★★ strong ≤1°</strong> / <strong style=\"color:#b8860b\">★ notable ≤2°</strong> (only for ±2° stars). A fixed star / natal planet or angle conjunction is a <em>permanent signature</em> of the chart.'\n          : 'Orbes appliqués : <strong>±2°</strong> pour Aldébaran, Sirius, Régulus, Spica, Antarès (étoiles royales/majeures) — <strong>±1°</strong> pour Algol, Pléiades, Véga, Fomalhaut. Précision : <strong style=\"color:#5d4037\">★★ forte ≤1°</strong> / <strong style=\"color:#b8860b\">★ notable ≤2°</strong> (uniquement pour les étoiles à ±2°). Une conjonction étoile fixe / planète ou angle natal est une <em>signature permanente</em> du thème.'}\n    </p>`;\n\n    if (etoileMatches.length > 0) {\n        html += `<h3 class=\"subsection-title\">${isEN ? 'Natal Planet / Fixed Star Conjunctions' : 'Conjonctions Planètes Natales / Étoiles Fixes'}</h3>`;\n        html += `<table>\n            <tr><th>${isEN ? 'Natal Planet' : 'Planète Natale'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Fixed Star' : 'Étoile Fixe'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'House' : 'Maison'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Sign' : 'Signe'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Orb' : 'Orbe'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Precision' : 'Précision'}</th></tr>`;\n        etoileMatches.forEach(em => {\n            const precColor  = em.precision.includes(\"forte\") ? \"#5d4037\" : \"#b8860b\";\n            const precSymbol = em.precision.includes(\"forte\") ? \"★★\" : \"★\";\n            const angleStyle = em.isAngle ? \" style=\\\"background:#fffbeb\\\"\" : \"\";\n            html += `<tr${angleStyle}>\n                <td><strong>${em.planete}</strong>${em.isAngle ? ' <small style=\"color:#5d4037\">[angle]</small>' : ''}</td>\n                <td>\n                    <strong style=\"color:#5d4037\">${em.etoile}</strong>\n                    <small style=\"color:#94a3b8;display:block\">${em.etoile_en}</small>\n                </td>\n                <td style=\"text-align:center;font-weight:bold;color:#5d4037\">M${em.maison}</td>\n                <td>${em.signe}</td>\n                <td style=\"text-align:center\">${em.orb}°</td>\n                <td style=\"text-align:center;font-weight:bold;color:${precColor}\">${precSymbol} ${em.precision.replace(\"forte (≤1°)\",\"forte\").replace(\"notable (≤2°)\",\"notable\")}</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr style=\"background:#fffbeb\">\n                <td colspan=\"6\" style=\"font-style:italic;color:#5d4037;font-size:0.88em;padding:6px 12px 10px\">${em.desc}</td>\n            </tr>`;\n        });\n        html += `</table>`;\n    }\n\n    if (etoileCuspMatches.length > 0) {\n        html += `<h3 class=\"subsection-title\">${isEN ? 'Fixed Stars on the 4 Angles (H1 ASC · H4 IC · H7 DSC · H10 MC)' : 'Étoiles Fixes sur les 4 Angles (M1 ASC · M4 IC · M7 DSC · M10 MC)'}</h3>`;\n        html += `<p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-size:0.9em;color:#64748b;font-style:italic;\">\n            ${isEN\n              ? 'A fixed star on an angle colors the fundamental identity of this chart pillar, regardless of any tenant. Its influence is decisive for the overall expression of the chart.'\n              : 'Une étoile fixe sur un angle teinte l\\'identité fondamentale de ce pilier du thème, indépendamment de tout locataire. Son influence est déterminante pour l\\'expression globale du thème.'}\n        </p>`;\n        html += `<table>\n            <tr><th>${isEN ? 'Angle' : 'Angle'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Fixed Star' : 'Étoile Fixe'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Cusp Sign' : 'Signe de la Cuspide'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Orb' : 'Orbe'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Precision' : 'Précision'}</th></tr>`;\n        etoileCuspMatches.forEach(ec => {\n            const precColor  = ec.precision.includes(\"forte\") ? \"#5d4037\" : \"#b8860b\";\n            const precSymbol = ec.precision.includes(\"forte\") ? \"★★\" : \"★\";\n            html += `<tr style=\"background:#fffbeb\">\n                <td><strong style=\"color:#5d4037\">M${ec.maison} — ${ec.angle}</strong></td>\n                <td>\n                    <strong style=\"color:#5d4037\">${ec.etoile}</strong>\n                    <small style=\"color:#94a3b8;display:block\">${ec.etoile_en}</small>\n                </td>\n                <td>${ec.signe}</td>\n                <td style=\"text-align:center\">${ec.orb}°</td>\n                <td style=\"text-align:center;font-weight:bold;color:${precColor}\">${precSymbol} ${ec.precision.replace(\"forte (≤1°)\",\"forte\").replace(\"notable (≤2°)\",\"notable\")}</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr style=\"background:#fffbeb\">\n                <td colspan=\"5\" style=\"font-style:italic;color:#5d4037;font-size:0.88em;padding:6px 12px 10px\">${ec.desc}</td>\n            </tr>`;\n        });\n        html += `</table>`;\n    }\n\n    if (paranResults.length > 0) {\n        html += `<h3 class=\"subsection-title\">${isEN ? 'Parans — Fixed Stars Co-Angularity (Brady Method)' : 'Parans — Co-angularité d\\'Étoiles Fixes (méthode Brady)'}</h3>`;\n        html += `<p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-size:0.9em;color:#64748b;font-style:italic;\">\n            ${isEN\n              ? 'A paran forms when a fixed star and a planet are simultaneously on a cardinal angle (rising, setting, culmination, or anti-culmination). It is a deep and permanent link, calculated according to geographic latitude.'\n              : 'Un paran se forme quand une étoile fixe et une planète se trouvent simultanément sur un angle cardinal (lever, coucher, culmination ou anti-culmination). C\\'est un lien profond et permanent, calculé selon la latitude géographique.'}\n        </p>`;\n        html += `<table>\n            <tr><th>${isEN ? 'Fixed Star' : 'Étoile Fixe'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Star Angle' : 'Angle Étoile'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Planet' : 'Planète'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Planet Angle' : 'Angle Planète'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'RAMC Orb' : 'Orbe RAMC'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Interpretation' : 'Interprétation'}</th></tr>`;\n        paranResults.forEach(pr => {\n            const orbColor = pr.orb <= 0.5 ? \"#5d4037\" : pr.orb <= 1.0 ? \"#b8860b\" : \"#94a3b8\";\n            html += `<tr style=\"background:#fffbeb\">\n                <td><strong style=\"color:#5d4037\">${pr.etoile}</strong></td>\n                <td style=\"text-align:center\">${pr.angle_etoile}</td>\n                <td><strong style=\"color:#5d4037\">${pr.planete}</strong> <small style=\"color:#94a3b8\">${pr.signe_planete || ''}</small></td>\n                <td style=\"text-align:center\">${pr.angle_planete}</td>\n                <td style=\"text-align:center;color:${orbColor};font-weight:bold\">${pr.orb}°</td>\n                <td style=\"font-size:0.88em;color:#5d4037;font-style:italic\">${pr.interpretation}</td>\n            </tr>`;\n            if (pr.etoile_desc) {\n                html += `<tr style=\"background:#fff8e1\">\n                    <td colspan=\"6\" style=\"font-size:0.85em;color:#5d4037;padding:4px 12px 8px;border-top:none\">${pr.etoile_desc.substring(0, 200)}</td>\n                </tr>`;\n            }\n        });\n        html += `</table>`;\n    }\n}\n\n// ── Antiscia et Contra-Antiscia (si présents) ──\nif (antiscia.length > 0) {\n    html += `<h2 class=\"section-title page-break\">${isEN ? 'Antiscia and Contra-Antiscia' : 'Antiscia et Contra-Antiscia'}</h2>`;\n    html += `<p style=\"color:#1F3864;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 12px;padding:10px 14px;background:#eef2fb;border-radius:6px;border-left:4px solid #2E5FA3;font-size:0.9em;\">\n        ${isEN\n          ? 'Antiscia are solar declination mirrors on the solstice axis (0° Cancer / 0° Capricorn). Two planets in antiscia share the same day length — a hidden connection acting as a subtle conjunction. Contra-Antiscia (mirror on the equinox axis) act as a discreet opposition. Orb applied: <strong>±1.5°</strong>.'\n          : 'Les Antiscia sont des miroirs de déclinaison solaire sur l\\'axe des solstices (0° Cancer / 0° Capricorne). Deux planètes en antiscia partagent la même durée de jour — connexion cachée agissant comme une conjonction subtile. Les Contra-Antiscia (miroir sur l\\'axe des équinoxes) agissent comme une opposition discrète. Orbe appliqué : <strong>±1.5°</strong>.'}\n    </p>`;\n    html += `<table>\n        <tr><th>${isEN ? 'Planet 1' : 'Planète 1'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Planet 2' : 'Planète 2'}</th><th>Type</th><th style=\"text-align:center\">${isEN ? 'Orb' : 'Orbe'}</th></tr>`;\n    antiscia.forEach(a => {\n        const isContra = a.type === \"Contra-antiscia\";\n        const typeStyle = isContra ? \"color:#1F3864;font-weight:bold\" : \"color:#2E5FA3;font-weight:bold\";\n        const rowBg = isContra ? ' style=\"background:#e8f0fe\"' : ' style=\"background:#eef2fb\"';\n        html += `<tr${rowBg}>\n            <td><strong>${a.p1}</strong></td>\n            <td><strong>${a.p2}</strong></td>\n            <td><span style=\"${typeStyle}\">${a.type}</span></td>\n            <td style=\"text-align:center\">${a.orb}°</td>\n        </tr>`;\n    });\n    html += `</table>`;\n}\n\n// ── Midpoints Activés (si présents) ──\nconst midpointActivations = input.midpointActivations || [];\nif (midpointActivations.length > 0) {\n    html += `<h2 class=\"section-title page-break\">${isEN ? 'Activated Midpoints' : 'Midpoints Activés'}</h2>`;\n    html += `<p style=\"color:#1F3864;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 12px;padding:10px 14px;background:#eef2fb;border-radius:6px;border-left:4px solid #2E5FA3;font-size:0.9em;\">\n        ${isEN\n          ? 'A midpoint is the median point between two planets. When a third planet transits or is natally on this midpoint (±1.5°), it <strong>activates</strong> the combination of the two planets and catalyzes their expression. Type <strong>direct</strong> = conjunction to midpoint; type <strong>mirror</strong> = opposition (same axis).'\n          : 'Un midpoint est le point médian entre deux planètes. Quand une troisième planète transite ou se trouve natalement sur ce midpoint (±1.5°), elle <strong>active</strong> la combinaison des deux planètes et en catalyse l\\'expression. Type <strong>direct</strong> = conjonction au midpoint ; type <strong>miroir</strong> = opposition (même axe).'}\n    </p>`;\n    html += `<table>\n        <tr><th>${isEN ? 'Activator' : 'Activateur'}</th><th>Midpoint</th><th>Type</th><th style=\"text-align:center\">${isEN ? 'Orb' : 'Orbe'}</th></tr>`;\n    midpointActivations.slice(0, 20).forEach(ma => {\n        const typeColor = ma.type === \"direct\" ? \"#1F3864\" : \"#2E5FA3\";\n        html += `<tr>\n            <td><strong>${ma.activator}</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#1F3864\">${ma.midpoint}</td>\n            <td><span style=\"color:${typeColor};font-weight:bold\">${ma.type === \"direct\" ? (isEN ? \"Direct (conjunction)\" : \"Direct (conjonction)\") : (isEN ? \"Mirror (opposition)\" : \"Miroir (opposition)\")}</span></td>\n            <td style=\"text-align:center\">${ma.orb}°</td>\n        </tr>`;\n    });\n    if (midpointActivations.length > 20) {\n        html += `<tr><td colspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#94a3b8;font-style:italic\">${isEN ? `... and ${midpointActivations.length - 20} other activations` : `... et ${midpointActivations.length - 20} autres activations`}</td></tr>`;\n    }\n    html += `</table>`;\n}\n\n// ── Lots Hermétiques (Sprint 7) ──\nconst SIGNS_ORDER = [\"Bélier\",\"Taureau\",\"Gémeaux\",\"Cancer\",\"Lion\",\"Vierge\",\"Balance\",\"Scorpion\",\"Sagittaire\",\"Capricorne\",\"Verseau\",\"Poissons\"];\nconst lotHouseCusps = (input.maisons || []).map(h => {\n    const csp = h.segments?.[0] || { signe: \"Bélier\", degre_debut: 0 };\n    return { house: h.maison, deg: (SIGNS_ORDER.indexOf(csp.signe) * 30 + csp.degre_debut) % 360 };\n}).sort((a,b) => a.deg - b.deg);\nconst findLotHouse = (fd) => {\n    for (let i = 0; i < 12; i++) {\n        const h1 = lotHouseCusps[i].deg, h2 = lotHouseCusps[(i+1)%12].deg;\n        if (h1 < h2) { if (fd >= h1 && fd < h2) return lotHouseCusps[i].house; }\n        else         { if (fd >= h1 || fd < h2) return lotHouseCusps[i].house; }\n    }\n    return \"?\";\n};\nconst LOTS_DISPLAY = [\n    {fr:\"Part de Fortune\",     en:\"Part of Fortune\",    desc: isEN ? \"Abundance, material success, positive flow\"          : \"Abondance, réussite matérielle, flux positif\", glyph:\"⊕\"},\n    {fr:\"Lot de l'Esprit\",     en:\"Lot of Spirit\",      desc: isEN ? \"Vocation, consciousness, soul path\"                  : \"Vocation, conscience, chemin de l'âme\", glyph:\"⊗\"},\n    {fr:\"Lot de Nécessité\",    en:\"Lot of Necessity\",   desc: isEN ? \"Constraints, unavoidable trials, karma\"              : \"Contraintes, épreuves inévitables, karma\", glyph:\"⊖\"},\n    {fr:\"Lot d'Éros\",          en:\"Lot of Eros\",        desc: isEN ? \"Passion, attraction, vital drive\"                    : \"Passion, attraction, élan vital\", glyph:\"♡\"},\n    {fr:\"Lot de Courage\",      en:\"Lot of Courage\",     desc: isEN ? \"Boldness, initiative, combative assertion\"           : \"Audace, initiative, affirmation combative\", glyph:\"⚔\"},\n    {fr:\"Lot de Némésis\",     