           : \"Déplacement, quête lointaine, exploration\", glyph:\"✢\"}\n];\nconst lotsInChart = LOTS_DISPLAY.filter(ld => (input.planetes || []).some(p => p.planet?.fr === ld.fr));\nif (lotsInChart.length > 0) {\n    html += `<h2 class=\"section-title page-break\">${isEN ? 'Hermetic Lots (Arabic Parts)' : 'Lots Hermétiques (Parts Arabes)'}</h2>`;\n    html += `<p style=\"color:#1F3864;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 12px;padding:10px 14px;background:#eef2fb;border-radius:6px;border-left:4px solid #2E5FA3;font-size:0.9em;\">\n        ${isEN\n          ? 'Hermetic Lots are mathematical points calculated from the Ascendant, Sun, Moon, and other planets. Each Lot activates a specific existential theme in the house and sign where it falls. Formulas: <strong>Fortune</strong> = ASC + Moon − Sun (diurnal); <strong>Spirit</strong> = inverse.'\n          : 'Les Lots hermétiques sont des points mathématiques calculés à partir de l\\'Ascendant, du Soleil, de la Lune et d\\'autres planètes. Chaque Lot active un thème existentiel spécifique dans la maison et le signe où il se trouve. Formules : <strong>Fortune</strong> = ASC + Lune − Soleil (diurne) ; <strong>Esprit</strong> = inverse.'}\n    </p>`;\n    html += `<table><tr><th>Lot</th><th style=\"text-align:center\">${isEN ? 'Glyph' : 'Glyphe'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Sign' : 'Signe'}</th><th style=\"text-align:center\">${isEN ? 'Degree' : 'Degré'}</th><th style=\"text-align:center\">${isEN ? 'House' : 'Maison'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Meaning' : 'Signification'}</th></tr>`;\n    lotsInChart.forEach(ld => {\n        const pObj = (input.planetes || []).find(p => p.planet?.fr === ld.fr);\n        if (!pObj) return;\n        const sign = pObj.zodiac_sign?.name?.fr || \"?\";\n        const deg = ((pObj.normDegree ?? pObj.fullDegree ?? 0) % 30).toFixed(2);\n        const house = findLotHouse(pObj.fullDegree);\n        html += `<tr>\n            <td><strong>${isEN ? (ld.en || ld.fr) : ld.fr}</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"text-align:center;font-size:1.3em\">${ld.glyph}</td>\n            <td>${sign}</td>\n            <td style=\"text-align:center\">${deg}°</td>\n            <td style=\"text-align:center;font-weight:bold;color:#1F3864\">M${house}</td>\n            <td style=\"font-size:0.9em;color:#64748b;font-style:italic\">${ld.desc}</td>\n        </tr>`;\n    });\n    html += `</table>`;\n}\n\n// ── Arbre des Dispositions et Dispositeur Final ──\nif (dispositorTree?.finalDispositors?.length > 0 || Object.keys(dispositorTree?.tree || {}).length > 0) {\n    const tree = dispositorTree.tree || {};\n    const finals = dispositorTree.finalDispositors || [];\n    html += `<h2 class=\"section-title page-break\">${isEN ? 'Dispositor Tree' : 'Arbre des Dispositions'}</h2>`;\n    html += `<p style=\"color:#1F3864;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 12px;padding:10px 14px;background:#eef2fb;border-radius:6px;border-left:4px solid #2E5FA3;font-size:0.9em;\">\n        ${isEN\n          ? 'The dispositor tree traces the rulership chain: each planet is \"commanded\" by the ruler of its sign. The final dispositor is the planet in domicile that concentrates the power of the entire chain.'\n          : 'L\\'arbre des dispositions trace la chaîne de maîtrise : chaque planète est « commandée » par le maître de son signe. Le dispositeur final est la planète en domicile qui concentre le pouvoir de toute la chaîne.'}\n    </p>`;\n    if (finals.length > 0) {\n        html += `<div style=\"background:#dbeafe;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:12px;font-weight:bold;color:#1e40af;font-size:1.05em\">\n            ${isEN ? 'Final Dispositor(s)' : 'Dispositeur(s) final(aux)'} : ${finals.join(\", \")}\n        </div>`;\n    }\n    html += `<table><tr><th>${isEN ? 'Planet' : 'Planète'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Rulership Chain' : 'Chaîne de maîtrise'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Final Dispositor' : 'Dispositeur final'}</th></tr>`;\n    Object.entries(tree).forEach(([name, data]) => {\n        const chainStr = data.chain.map(c => c.inDomicile ? `<strong style=\"color:#1e40af\">${c.planet}</strong>` : c.planet).join(\" → \");\n        html += `<tr><td><strong>${name}</strong></td><td>${chainStr}</td><td style=\"text-align:center;font-weight:bold;color:#1e40af\">${data.finalDispositor || `<span style=\"color:#94a3b8\">∞ ${isEN ? 'loop' : 'boucle'}</span>`}</td></tr>`;\n    });\n    html += `</table>`;\n}\n\n// ── Dignité Accidentelle (Lilly) ──\nif (accidentalDignity.length > 0) {\n    html += `<h2 class=\"section-title page-break\">${isEN ? 'Accidental Dignity (Lilly)' : 'Force Planétaire — Dignité Accidentelle (Lilly)'}</h2>`;\n    html += `<p style=\"color:#1F3864;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 12px;padding:10px 14px;background:#eef2fb;border-radius:6px;border-left:4px solid #2E5FA3;font-size:0.9em;\">\n        ${isEN\n          ? 'Score combining essential dignity (domicile, exaltation, detriment, fall) and accidental dignity (house, motion, heliocentric conditions, receptions). A high score (&gt;15) = major chart actor. A negative score = impeded planet.'\n          : 'Score combinant dignité essentielle (domicile, exaltation, exil, chute) et accidentelle (maison, mouvement, conditions héliocentriques, réceptions). Un score élevé (&gt;15) = acteur majeur du thème. Un score négatif = planète empêchée.'}\n    </p>`;\n    html += `<table><tr><th>${isEN ? 'Planet' : 'Planète'}</th><th style=\"text-align:center\">Score</th><th>${isEN ? 'Details' : 'Détail'}</th></tr>`;\n    accidentalDignity.forEach(d => {\n        const color = d.score >= 15 ? '#166534' : d.score >= 8 ? '#1e40af' : d.score >= 0 ? '#475569' : '#991b1b';\n        html += `<tr><td><strong>${d.planet}</strong></td><td style=\"text-align:center;font-weight:bold;color:${color};font-size:1.1em\">${d.score}</td>\n        <td style=\"font-size:0.85em;color:#64748b\">${(d.details || []).join(\" · \")}</td></tr>`;\n    });\n    html += `</table>`;\n}\n\n// ── Conditions spéciales : Hayz, Assiégées, VOC Lune ──\nif (hayzPlanets.length > 0 || besiegedPlanets.length > 0 || moonVOC) {\n    html += `<h2 class=\"section-title page-break\">${isEN ? 'Special Conditions' : 'Conditions Spéciales'}</h2>`;\n    if (hayzPlanets.length > 0) {\n        html += `<div class=\"subsection-title\">✦ ${isEN ? 'Hayz (optimal sect condition)' : 'Hayz (condition de secte optimale)'}</div>`;\n        hayzPlanets.forEach(h => {\n            html += `<div style=\"padding:6px 12px;margin:4px 0;background:#eef2fb;border-left:3px solid #2E5FA3;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.92em\">${h.description}</div>`;\n        });\n    }\n    if (besiegedPlanets.length > 0) {\n        html += `<div class=\"subsection-title\">⚠ ${isEN ? 'Besieged Planets' : 'Planètes Assiégées'}</div>`;\n        besiegedPlanets.forEach(b => {\n            html += `<div style=\"padding:6px 12px;margin:4px 0;background:#fef2f2;border-left:3px solid #dc2626;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.92em\">${b.description}</div>`;\n        });\n    }\n    if (moonVOC) {\n        html += `<div class=\"subsection-title\">◯ ${isEN ? 'Void of Course Moon' : 'Lune Vide de Course'}</div>`;\n        html += `<div style=\"padding:6px 12px;margin:4px 0;background:#eef2fb;border-left:3px solid #2E5FA3;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.92em\">${moonVOC.description}</div>`;\n    }\n    const stationaryPlanetsR = input.stationaryPlanets || [];\n    if (stationaryPlanetsR.length > 0) {\n        html += `<div class=\"subsection-title\">⏸ ${isEN ? 'Stationary Planets (concentrated energy)' : 'Planètes Stationnaires (énergie concentrée)'}</div>`;\n        stationaryPlanetsR.forEach(sp => {\n            html += `<div style=\"padding:6px 12px;margin:4px 0;background:#eef2fb;border-left:3px solid #2E5FA3;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.92em\">\n                <strong>${sp.planet}</strong> — ${sp.direction} ${isEN ? 'in' : 'en'} ${sp.sign} (${isEN ? 'H' : 'M'}${sp.house}) — ${isEN ? 'speed' : 'vitesse'} ${sp.speed}°/${isEN ? 'day' : 'jour'} (${isEN ? 'threshold' : 'seuil'} ${sp.threshold}°/${isEN ? 'day' : 'jour'}).\n                ${isEN ? 'A stationary planet concentrates its energy exceptionally — first-order marker.' : 'Une planète stationnaire concentre son énergie de manière exceptionnelle — marqueur de premier ordre.'}\n            </div>`;\n        });\n    }\n}\n\n// ── Degrés Sabian ──\nif (Object.keys(sabianData).length > 0) {\n    html += `<h2 class=\"section-title page-break\">${isEN ? 'Sabian Degrees' : 'Degrés Sabian'}</h2>`;\n    html += `<p style=\"color:#1F3864;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 12px;padding:10px 14px;background:#eef2fb;border-radius:6px;border-left:4px solid #2E5FA3;font-size:0.9em;\">\n        ${isEN\n          ? 'Each degree of the zodiac has an image symbol (Marc Edmund Jones / Dane Rudhyar). These images offer a poetic and symbolic nuance of the planetary position.'\n          : 'Chaque degré du zodiaque possède un symbole imagé (Marc Edmund Jones / Dane Rudhyar). Ces images offrent une nuance poétique et symbolique de la position planétaire.'}\n    </p>`;\n    html += `<table><tr><th>${isEN ? 'Planet' : 'Planète'}</th><th style=\"text-align:center\">${isEN ? 'Degree' : 'Degré'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Sign' : 'Signe'}</th><th>${isEN ? 'Sabian Symbol' : 'Symbole Sabian'}</th></tr>`;\n    Object.entries(sabianData).forEach(([name, data]) => {\n        html += `<tr><td><strong>${name}</strong></td><td style=\"text-align:center\">${data.degree}°</td><td>${data.sign}</td>\n        <td style=\"font-style:italic;color:#475569\">« ${data.symbol} »</td></tr>`;\n    });\n    html += `</table>`;\n}\n\n// ── Profil de sensibilité ──\nif (sensitivityProfileR) {\n    html += `<h2 class=\"section-title page-break\">${isEN ? 'Chart Sensitivity Profile' : 'Profil de Sensibilité du Thème'}</h2>`;\n    html += `<p style=\"color:#1F3864;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 12px;padding:10px 14px;background:#eef2fb;border-radius:6px;border-left:4px solid #2E5FA3;font-size:0.9em;\">\n        ${isEN\n          ? 'This profile identifies the elemental vulnerabilities and familiarities of the chart, as well as the modal dispositions that condition receptivity to transits.'\n          : 'Ce profil identifie les vulnérabilités et familiarités élémentaires du thème, ainsi que les dispositions modales qui conditionnent la réceptivité aux transits.'}\n    </p>`;\n    sensitivityProfileR.split('\\n').filter(Boolean).forEach(line => {\n        const isVuln = line.includes('VULNÉRABILITÉ');\n        const isFam = line.includes('FAMILIARITÉ');\n        const bg = isVuln ? '#fef2f2' : isFam ? '#eef2fb' : '#e8f0fe';\n        const border = isVuln ? '#dc2626' : isFam ? '#2E5FA3' : '#1F3864';\n        html += `<div style=\"padding:8px 14px;margin:4px 0;background:${bg};border-left:3px solid ${border};border-radius:4px;font-size:0.92em\">${line}</div>`;\n    });\n}\n\nhtml += `</div></body></html>`;\n\nreturn [{\n    json: { success: true },\n    binary: {\n        html_file: {\n            data: Buffer.from(html, 'utf8').toString('base64'),\n            mimeType: 'text/html',\n            fileName: `index.html`\n        }\n    }\n}];\n} catch (_globalErr) {\n    const errHtml = `<html><body style=\"font-family:sans-serif;padding:40px\"><h1 style=\"color:#dc2626\">${isEN ? 'Report generation error' : 'Erreur de génération du rapport'}</h1><p>${_globalErr.message}</p><pre>${_globalErr.stack}</pre></body></html>`;\n    return [{ json: { error: true, message: _globalErr.message }, binary: { html_file: { data: Buffer.from(errHtml,'utf8').toString('base64'), mimeType:'text/html', fileName:'error.html' } } }];\n}"
